description: Welcome to the "Edison on First" created in 2017 by one of South Boston's most reputable developers. Residence C6 offers an expansive kitchen & living room open floor plan ideal for entertaining, including an attached private deck (7x22) gas lined for grilling. The chef's kitchen features brilliant white quartz countertops & island, commercial grade Wolf/Sub Zero appliances, beautifully detailed coffered ceilings, European styled cabinetry plus wet bar. The master bedroom includes a large walk-in closet enhanced with LED recessed lighting and en-suite bath with dual vanity, steam shower and a generously sized soaking tub. Both baths include tiled floors & showers, quartz countertops and chrome accents. The 2nd bedroom is large in size with plenty of closet space. Multiple options throughout the home for office/work space. Deeded private roof deck space overlooking the downtown Boston skyline. Two deeded garage parking and one deeded storage unit (5x6).
